Artist and creative innovator with background as performance designer. Central Saint Martins graduate and Royal College of Arts Master in History of Design and Material Culture. Now creating NFTs transcending our common vision of reality.

With Moody Aliens she touches upon the untouched, the vision of tomorrow, showing emotions of today.

Sofia goes by the artist name Lilpix.

Moody Aliens started as a collection of biro drawings on paper and developed into digital works of art. Moody Aliens are an exploration of what the future human kind will look like when we become interplanetary species.

features.text: TALK Concept: All songs in one

Fashion Hat Punks is an on-chain PFP collection that invites us to imagine a world in which all 10,000 original CryptoPunks wore fashionable hats but otherwise looked the same.

Because it is stored entirely on the Ethereum blockchain, your Fashion Hat Punk's image and metadata cannot be deleted, restricted, or tampered with in any way. It will also never go out of style! However, for added peace of mind, the collection was carefully designed to not imply affiliation with any potentially-litigious rightsholder.

And for added-added peace of mind, I'm going to come right out and say (though it is entirely unecessary): Fashion Hat Punks are not affiliated with Larva Labs, Yuga Labs, any fashion brand, Punk-derivative collection, or work of readymade art, including Marcel Duchamp's L.H.O.O.Q.

What would you say if you knew it would last forever?

Forever Message is an Ethereum-based application that allows anyone to send messages that cannot be deleted, restricted, or tampered with in any way. All of your Forever Messages will be available forever to the entire world exactly as you composed them.

There is no limit to the number of Forever Messages that can be sent, so send a message that lasts forever today!

The gallery consists of multiple rooms exhibiting new music & art, digital NFTs, live concerts and much more.
